            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》紫金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02899:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02899\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02899-HK</a>)H股現價升2.5%,報16.48元,以現價計,該股暫連升2日,累計升幅6%。該股成交約1619萬股,涉資2.65億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　美國關稅不確定性因素持續令市場不安,憂慮高關稅將會引發通脹升溫,避險需求提升帶動金價上漲,隔晚紐約期金再升近1%,於2950美元關口前徘徊,現報約2945美元。港股<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>ETF　SPDR金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02840:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02840\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02840-HK</a>)現升0.8%,報2103元。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　金礦股造好;山東<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01787:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01787\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01787-HK</a>)升1%,報15.96元;招金礦業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01818:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01818\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01818-HK</a>)升0.3%,報14.24元;靈寶<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(一千)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.c